<section class="rbp-brandpg-sec"><div class="rbp-brandpg-c"><div class="rbp-brandpg-head"><div class="rbp-brandpg-ey">Trust markers</div><h2 class="rbp-brandpg-h2">What customers should expect</h2></div><div class="rbp-brandpg-grid rbp-brandpg-g4"><div class="rbp-brandpg-card"><div class="rbp-brandpg-stat">01</div><div class="rbp-brandpg-stat-label">Plain-English guidance and practical next steps</div></div><div class="rbp-brandpg-card"><div class="rbp-brandpg-stat">02</div><div class="rbp-brandpg-stat-label">Structured pathways for documents, services and support</div></div><div class="rbp-brandpg-card"><div class="rbp-brandpg-stat">03</div><div class="rbp-brandpg-stat-label">Business-owner focused resources and support routes</div></div><div class="rbp-brandpg-card"><div class="rbp-brandpg-stat">04</div><div class="rbp-brandpg-stat-label">Connected experience across store, Help Center and services</div></div></div></div></section>
